Those who prefer to save money and that the quality of accommodation in second place, which can try to wait a few more days.
The hotel of Špindler offer for the moment that stays a week for the New Year.
I think that they will seek to sell them for a while, but they also and accept shorter periods.
And then the free rooms will be quickly, estimated Jandura.
