The People are waiting to see whether there will be snow.
No one wants to spend the winter in the mountains without snow.
If the runways overlap during the week, Christmas will be complete, " think Schiefert.
On the contrary, it is a little easier to fill the rooms in the hotel higher than last year.
We are about five percent better.
