United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is comical that Barack Obama, the president with the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan question, which he considered himself as simple.
When he finally revealed its Afghan approach, eagerly awaited, it showed that he is a copy of the script used in Iraq by Bush, created three years ago.
Not content to use in the text several times the expression " as in Iraq ", but do not hesitate to use the title of Bush's statement of January 2007 as the title of his own speech: " a new way forward "
At the same time, he has personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new military reinforcements to Iraq, by the civil war as " irresponsible and a disastrous decision in its consequences. "
The following month, however, showed that the Bush strategy, based on the recommendations of captains, was the only possible and do not speak today in the news about Iraq.
This has not improved the reputation of Bush, however objectively left to his successor a initial situation much more favourable than expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama hopes to repeat the miracle.
In order to increase the contingent have asked the military It again, including the commander of the Afghan operation General Stanley McCristal, even despite the trench in the White House.
He called for 40,000 men in order to improve the situation.
The president has hesitated for three months, but in the absence of a better option, at least misled the general about 10,000 soldiers.
From Europe, has the promise for a further 5,000, even though He himself.
The most problems throughout the strategy Obama seems to be its intention to withdraw troops from Afghanistan in 18 months and finish this process within three years. The doctrine of Obama raises more questions than answers.
Many doubt that the increase in the same fruit that the procedure in Iraq.
Despite the fratricidal wars in recent years, the society of Iraq is relatively well organised, their leaders to respect the agreements.
The Afghan situation in Afghanistan is different: it is not possible to rely on anyone and no agreement is respected.
Under these conditions, it is difficult to prepare the Afghan security forces, if they are used to change the head every day.
The political institutions, although formally established, will remain just a Potemkin smokescreen behind which will proliferate patriarchal ethnic relations.
Balancing the interests of various ethnic groups is unusually complicated, particularly because of the even more complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Even the foundation of a " state quick to act ", which is the aim of the operation, does not appear to be very real.
The time horizon of the Obama strategy perplexed by his voluntarism.
Over the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and is currently on the brink of chaos.
Only a romantic soul, to believe that the small soldiers in the war cry about the " reality can be sent soon return home " will bring a miracle.
From a political point of view, set the date for the withdrawal of troops is pure irresponsibility, because the Taliban will see this as the indirect confession of the American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the will of Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan.
European politicians do not know, and do not want to explain to their constituents, what the security of Germany or Italy with the war with the Hindu Kush.
Another factor that can radically alter the situation is the development of events in Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the US will have to make a difficult decision: try to solve the problem with military force or not.
It will be necessary to respond by example when, according to Obama, America will the victorious withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
However, every solution will mean a dramatic setback for the Afghan situation.
The only positive point for Barack Obama is the fact that there are three years until the presidential election and therefore there is still enough time to working on a new strategy, if it is a total failure.
The managers of the bank Goldman Sachs will receive no bonuses in cash
The chief executives of the US bank Goldman Sachs will receive no bonuses this year more in cash.
The company announced in response to strong criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 senior managers will receive, instead of money can sell shares, but only in five years.
In addition, The actions can be withdrawn in the event that they would take too many risks.
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs thus became the leader in the effort to link the bonuses with long - term performance on Wall Street.
I suppose that Wall Street is well aware of the overall sense that we must take, mentioned the former investment banker of society's, Douglas Elliott.
The problem is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs became the target of criticism after set aside almost $17 billion in premiums for the first three quarters of this year.
For this year, the total amount of premiums bonuses in the will probably exceed $20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters.
The high premiums bonuses in the banking sector became, With the arrival of the financial crisis, in a sensitive political issue in many countries.
Britain announced Wednesday that it plans to tax at once, with a tax of 50 per cent, the bonuses exceeding 25,000 pounds.
France is also preparing similar measures.
This year, women received the Nobel Prizes in all areas except the physical
Five women, which is a record number, received today in Stockholm in the hands of the King of Sweden this year's Nobel prizes in the technical categories and for literature.
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer of Romanian origin Herta Müller.
The Nobel Prize for Medicine have Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider, together with her compatriot Jack Szostak for research in the field of chromosomes.
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarification of the structure and function of the ribosomas.
The last winner received the Nobel Prize for economics, the American Elinor Ostrom and his compatriot Oliver Williamson for their analysis of the economic report.
The only specialist category, without a woman, was physics.
This prize was presented today scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith with Willard Boyle for the invention of the chip, which are the basis of all digital cameras, fax or telescopes.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of the money received.
This amount in each category is up to 10 million Swedish kronor (approximately 1.1 million euros) .
If one of them has several winners, they will share the prize them.
The much - anticipated Nobel Peace Prize has this afternoon in Oslo, Norway, US President Barack Obama.
In his speech acknowledged the controversial nature of his reward since it is only at the beginning of his career and is also at the head of a country engaged in two wars in Iraq and Afghanistan.
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential to achieve peace, even if the price is high.
