We do not feel like orphans, we are not small children, then he responded to the question of whether the ODS had not the absence of the head of the party in Parliament and in the Czech Republic, during the negotiations on the budget.
I have not noticed that my vote would lack.
As I withdrew To the mandate, I knew that in the following months in particular would be a bolchévisation of the House and the destruction of everything positive, reacted Topolánek.
According to the new schedule of the ČD there will be fewer trains for the same charges.
The Czech Railways will remove or limit from 13 December some express trains regional or less responsible and used and, on the contrary, strengthen some links.
The total length of transport volume will be reduced from the day of entry into force of the new schedule of two percent compared to today.
Most of the charges will not change, including the basic price and the reduced rate.
For example, the inhabitants of the Ostrava region who have more links to the capital, the railways will add a rowing pendolino.
The direct train, On the contrary, will not move to Bratislava.
There will also be less fast trains on the line Prague - Písek - České Budějovice, the direct links Prague - Letohrad.
In the regions, the largest decrease in transport is in the region of Hradec Králové eight percent in total, to an increase in Prague and environment.
Two night trains on the Prague - Tábor - České Budějovice are also cancelled and some fast trains in the line Prague - Pisek - České Budějovice will be reduced to only a few days the week.
One of the biggest changes is the introduction of a new line of Milovice to Prague, the inhabitants of Milovice must change in Lysá nad Labem.
It is the fifteenth line of the commuter system Esko, whose opening is possible thanks to the completion of the electrification of the line of Lysá nad Labem and Milovice.
The links to long distances to the capital will end up in the station Prague Hlavní nádraží.
The ČD will introduce more lines SC Pendolino between Prague and Ostrava and trains to Šumperk/Jeseník move every two hours.
Travellers can no longer take the Pendolino to Bratislava from 13 December.
The bill this year for regional railways: 200 million more than before
The fast trains are ordered and paid by the Ministry of Transport, to cover the so - called the railways next year in all four billion kronor the same amount as this year. Local trains are ordered by the regions, next year will pay eight billion kronor in total, and the state will help them almost three billion.
This year the regional trains are 200 million more expensive.
For The railways have newly signed a contract for ten years, until now the was always a year.
The railway the system, which also explains that they have not to the increase in the price of the vast majority of tickets.
The changes will affect only tickets a day ČD net and cheap tickets on the Internet eLiška.
For passengers without the customer card will increase the price of ČD net of 450 kroner to 600 kronor.
The price of eLiška will depend on the distance, until now there was a single price of 160 kroner for travel between any two regional cities.
The Filipino rebels still hold more than 50 people, The children were released
The gunmen have kidnapped today in the southern Philippines 75 people, including some of a primary school pupils and their teachers.
The agency AFP, which originally only about 65 Entführte informed.
The 17 children were released after eight hours, including a teacher.
The abduction occurred in the province of Agusan del Sur.
It is reported that about 19 rebels have used the hostages as human shields during a flight to the police.
The local negotiators are trying to find an agreement for the release of the remaining hostages.
According to the AFP agency, the rebels belong to the New People's Army (NPA) , which is the armed wing of the Communist Party of the Philippines (CPP) .
According to the AFP agency the police initially pursued the kidnappers because of the violence, which was the cause a settling of accounts between two family clans.
Martial law was declared in the province of Maguindanao in the southern Philippines because of a recent massacre in which 57 people were killed.
Among the victims of the massacre of 23 November, related to the election to the administration of the Governor, 30 journalists.
The suspicion of involvement in the massacre arrested the governor of the province in the southern Philippines and his father Andal Ampatuan, patriarch of the influential Ampatuan.
On The island of Mindanao also includes Muslim separatists.
However on Tuesday renewed peace talks with the Philippine government.
The history of South Africa affects everyone, says Morgan Freeman alias Mandela
In The next few days, the new Hollywood film Clint Eastwood US cinemas a Invictus (his official title in Czech: Neporažený) , which captures a part of the biography of the former President of the Republic of South Africa, Nelson Mandela.
The role of the world - famous fighter against apartheid is Morgan Freeman, who chose years ago by Mandela himself to embody.
The second male role of the legendary champion South African rugby has been attributed to Matt Damon.
With the arrival of the film in cinemas, the critics and the public are heard.
Nelson Mandela
Its full name is Nelson Rolihlahla Mandela, he was born on 18 July 1918 in South Africa.
In 1988 he was awarded the Sakharov Prize for freedom of spirit, in 1993, alongside de Klerk, the Nobel Peace Prize.
He was President of the Republic of South Africa from 1994 to 1999.
The film contains great expectations since it comes at a time when the South Africa is in full preparations for the World Cup, and secondly because the media are agitated by disturbing news about the growing racial hatred and discrimination of the inhabitants of the part of the black majority.
According to the news agency AP are the reactions to the new film in South Africa for the time being consistently positive, despite many reservations about the distribution of the main roles where " pavanent " Hollywood stars.
