A decision that in fact the first woman to hold a high position in the food companies.
It is a newly created position that will report directly to the president of the group.
And it is not without controversy, as the company remains submerged in the legal battle for the alleged embezzlement of more than 230 million of SOS to other societies of the Salazar.
In fact, it cannot be ruled out that in the next few months SOS reveals new misappropriation of funds
On the credit to Salazar, former advisers Ildefonso Ortega and Ángel Fernández Noriega (representatives of CCM and Unicaja) before the national Audience that they had approved the diversion of 212 million without knowing their destination.
The CNMV authorizes the takeover of exclusion of Paternina presented Mer
The National stock market Commission (CNMV) authorized yesterday the takeover bid of exclusion presented by on Federico Paternina on 9 October.
The supervisory body said that it authorized this operation to understand that its terms are in line with the existing rules and consider " sufficient " the content of the explanatory Beiblatts, after the changes on 2 December.
The CNMV said that the offer for the acquisition of 550,008 shares of Federico Paternina at a price of 7.65 euros per share, which represents 8.95% of social capital, composed of 6 142 786 shares admitted to trading on the stock exchanges in Madrid and Bilbao.
It was also explained that have been 5.592.778 million shares, which can be transmitted in any way until the completion of the offer, which has specified that the price has been set by Federico Paternina, in accordance with the provisions of the rules in force.
New tools for peritar cars
In these days of bad weather and accidents, not only earn the workshops of cars.
Every day, thousands of cars that have suffered a sinister are reduced to a garage, where an expert to assess the damage and the cost of the repair.
Every disaster is different, and the calculation of the cost of parts and the time of labour can be a long and complicated task.
Calcularmanualmente the cost of compensation of between 20,000 and 30,000 euros, including parts and labor can take two or three hours.
Instead, with the support of the latest computer tools, it would be a matter of minutes.
It is for this reason that almost 100% of the experts used this type of systems.
The Suppliers of services and solutions for the assessment of claims and maintenance are dedicated to collect the information provided by the manufacturers, and then treat them and offer their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex, the American group, is the market leader; 80% of the assessments are made with their products.
The other firms competing in the field of evaluation tools and the development of information on the sector are GtMotive and Eurotax.
The work with the data provided by manufacturers is far from simple.
According to Eduardo Velázquez, commercial director of Audatex, the company in Spain with 63 manufacturers and importers, and each of them provides information in a different format.
In addition, the amount of data to treat continues to the point that in the last five years, more versions, variants and motorisations have been launched in the past fifteen years.
As soon as a new car on the market, these companies are put to work.
It is a very hard work, because it each thousand pieces of the vehicle and its price.
In addition, it establishes a graphic image " intelligent " of each model on which you can click on the different parts of tourism.
If it is a model of ventamasiva, the work can be completed in a week if the process is moving very fast.
If it is a car sold, it can take three or four months. Currently, Audatex have full information on 99.2% of the cars in Spain.
Among the most exclusive models, they have, for example, information on the Porsche, but not the Ferrari or Lamborghini.
The vehicles in circulation, the figure exceeds 99%.
To do the job of documentation and development of databases, Audatex has eight centres around the world (Spain, France, Germany, the United States, Brazil, Mexico, China and Japan) , and each of them is specialised in certain brands.
The national headquarters is located in Alcobendas (Madrid) .
There, more than a hundred technicians (usually experts in mechanical) work simultaneously with three computer screens.
Audatex invested $90 million per year to develop these databases.
Each month, 2.5 million data are recorded, and customers receive updates every two days.
The development of this enormous flow of information allows these companies to give them different uses and offer varied products.
The most common application for the repair and maintenance, but depending on the country, there are also tools for the management of scrapping or to calculate the residual value of a car.
The only company that has a guide that tells about the value of used cars in Spain is Eurotax.
Audatex not offered in our country, but in the United States.
In view of the products offered by Audatex, it is easy to get an idea of the kind of support they can provide to professionals in the sector.
This company offers ten different tools, the flagship product Audaplus, the standard solution of assessment of claims, for the experts.
It involves vehicles, motorcycles and light and heavy industry vehicles.
In addition to the cost of the parts, it contains the times of repairs estimated by the manufacturer or the standards of paint.
This tool is paid according to use, for each assessment.
The higher cost is $5.75 euros, for customers who use little, a maximum of ten times a month.
Then, each insurance company, which conducts thousands of expertise, is negotiating a price with Audatex.
Other products, such as Audavin, allow the identification of a vehicle and equipment with which it came out of the assembly line, only through its chassis number.
Audaglass focuses on the glasses of vehicles, and Audasubastas is a service open to the professional sector on the Internet which allows for vehicles that wrecks.
Its statistics service is very useful for identifying trends, analyses géo - démographiques or know the problems by brand or model.
It is possible to study, for example, how many models of a particular mark went to the garage for a breakdown or how many have suffered serious losses for a given period.
GT motives is the only Spanish company dedicated to the development of this type of tools.
It sells, among others, GT estimate, which is also intended to experts and provides digital images, access to parts or prices and official times of the manufacturer.
GT motives is a company of the group Einsa, founded in 1971 as a provider of services and solutions for the assessment of damage, breakdowns or maintenance.
The GT guide evaluation is a historical reference product on the market.
The company works with 24,000 users in garages, experts and 53 insurance companies.
Its volume of business has grown at a rate of 20% per year over the last three years, and has a turnover of EUR 10.8 million in 2008.
At the beginning of last year, they began the process of internationalisation, with the establishment of an office in Paris.
For its part, Audatex was born in Germany in 1966 and in 1979 was established in Spain.
According to the sources of the company 62% of its business is generated in Europe and the rest of the world, and the remaining 38% in North and South America. Working with 900 insurance companies and 33,000 workshops, 3,000 of them in Spain.
The global turnover of the group (Audatex, Sidexa, Informex ABZ, Hollander and IMS) will amount to $557 million, 3.3% more than in 2008.
In our country, the company 19.1 million euros, 7.2% more than In the previous year.
In 2005, the group Solera was worth $1 billion in the stock market today, its shares are valued at a total of $2.4 billion.
Since 2007, in the New York Stock Exchange and is part of the benchmark Standard& Poor's.
Internet auction of cars
Last October, the group bought Autoonline, an Internet platform for the sale of cars, motorcycles and special vehicles.
The operation was a disbursement of 59.5 million for 85% of the company's capital, which could be extended next year to the remaining 15%.
The purpose of the acquisition was to provide more value - added services to its customers, with the possibility of access to a huge international market.
This service and sale is intended exclusively for professionals in the sector, such as insurance companies, experts, car rental companies, workshops, scrapping and sellers professionals who must be registered before starting to carry out operations.
This platform was created in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of them in Germany.
Among its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
The website has more than 1,500 registered buyers and 4,000 experts.
It manages 3,000 ads by day and on the Spanish market, 100 new announcements are published every day.
According to the Spanish law, a car whose chassis number has been withdrawn can no longer move, but they can be used as a spare parts that are not damaged parts.
The cars with historical value can be high even though they have been withdrawn, after complex.
Cost estimates of workshop in four stages
With the tool Auda - taller, the company Audatex ensures that the user gets a budget in only four steps: identify the vehicle, seek the parts, create a quotation and generate.
The ease of use is an essential element of these systems, especially to convince the older professionals, to a greater or lesser extent, are reluctant to use new management techniques.
The database includes 1,034 vehicles, which are 666 cars, 109, 137 motorcycles, 78 vans and 44 trucks.
Of course, you need to use a computer and an Internet connection.
Once identified the model to repair through its chassis number, a graphic image of the model in question and then you select the necessary.
The user can include variables such as the price of labour, increases or reductions, and then it can print the specifications for the client.
Audataller is not a tool of assessment as Audaplus, but rather a catalogue of references.
The main difference between the two systems is that the garages does not include the time of labour estimated.
The cost of using this tool for the workshop is of 350 per year, which the customer can finance.
Currently, the company Audatex is working to ensure that these images are in three - dimensional.
It is an innovation that mechanics are very good eye, as it will, for example, to select a door and turn to see the inner.
